Did you know?
-------------
- The National Vaccine Compensation Program has awarded over $3 billion in damages to children and adults injured by vaccines. (See page 4)

- Unusual high-pitched crying after vaccination is often a sign of brain inflammation. (See page 5)

- "A single vaccine given to a six pound newborn is equivalent to giving a 180-pound adult 30 vaccinations on the same day!"
(Dr. Boyd Haley, professor and chair, Dept, of Chemistry, University of Kentucky, 2001)

- The DTaP vaccine package insert lists both SIDS and autism as possible adverse reactions, and that 70% of SIDS deaths occur within 3 weeks after the vaccine. (See pages 7 and 32)

- After vaccine recommendations were accelerated in 1991, autism rates in the U.S. went up from roughly 4 in 2500 to at least 1 in 45 today) (See page 25)

- The CDC admits that no long-term studies were ever done on vaccines (See page 6)

- Getting a flu shot during pregnancy can increase the risk of miscarriage by 4,25% (See page 20)

- Vaccines contain known carcinogens (including formaldehyde and polysorbate
80) and childhood cancers are continuously climbing (See box on page S)

